# ============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS - Automatic Review Assignment
# ============================================================================
# GitHub automatically requests reviews from code owners when PRs modify
# files they own. Code owners must have write access to the repository.
#
# Syntax:
#   pattern  @owner1 @owner2 @org/team-name
#
# Later rules take precedence. Use * for default ownership.
# ============================================================================

